I'm sorry about your grandmother, Carnage.

::Prowl::

Prowl shruggs. "We're not going through there anyways."

He steps onto Dinobot's tail, then jumping lightly to his shoulders. Being a 
flyer, he wasn't too heavy. He reaches up, sliding the vent aside and jumping 
into it, his arms pulling him up. On the inside, the vent was pretty big, 
enough room to acomodate Prowl and Dinobot. Prowl reaches down, holding a 
hand out for Dinobot to grab onto.
